events.name: New York Knicks at Charlotte Hornets

headlines.description: — Jalen Brunson had 31 points and made two clutch free throws with 8.6 seconds left, and the New York Knicks held on to beat the shorthanded Charlotte Hornets 99-98 to improve to 3-0 in <a...
headlines.shortLinkText: Jalen Brunson pours in 31 points as Knicks hold on to beat the Hornets 99-98 in NBA Cup play

headlines.description: — De'Andre Hunter scored 23 points off Atlanta's bench and the Hawks beat Cleveland 117-101 on Friday in the NBA Cup, handing the Cavaliers a loss for the second time in three days.
headlines.shortLinkText: De'Andre Hunter scores 23 points as the Hawks beat the NBA-best Cavs again, 117-101

events.name: New Orleans Pelicans at Memphis Grizzlies

headlines.description: — Ja Morant had 27 points and seven assists as the Memphis Grizzlies beat the injury-riddled New Orleans Pelicans 120-109 on Friday evening for their first NBA Cup win in franchise history.
headlines.shortLinkText: Grizzlies beat Pelicans 120-109 for 1st NBA Cup win in franchise history

headlines.description: — Franz Wagner scored 29 points, Kentavious Caldwell-Pope added 19 and the Orlando Magic eased to a 123-100 victory over the Brooklyn Nets on Friday night in an NBA Cup game.
headlines.shortLinkText: Franz Wagner's 29 points propel Magic to 123-100 NBA Cup win over Nets

headlines.description: — Anthony Edwards scored 21 points on 7-for-21 shooting to help the Minnesota...
headlines.shortLinkText: Timberwolves stop 4-game losing streak by fending off Clippers 93-92 in NBA Cup play

headlines.description: — Cade Cunningham had 24 points and 11 rebounds in his return from a three-game absence, Jaden Ivey added 23 points and the Detroit Pistons beat the Indiana Pacers 130-106 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cade Cunningham has 24 points, 11 rebounds in return and Pistons beat Pacers 130-106

headlines.description: — Jimmy Butler scored 26 points, Tyler Herro added 23 and the Miami Heat beat the Toronto Raptors 121-111 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Butler scores 26, Herro adds 23 and Adebayo has triple-double as Miami tops Toronto 121-111

headlines.description: — Jayson Tatum scored 35 points and had 14 rebounds to lead the Boston Celtics past the Chicago Bulls 138-129 in Friday night’s NBA Cup pool game.
headlines.shortLinkText: Tatum scores 35, Pritchard adds 29 off the bench and Celtics outlast Bulls 138-129

events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — Shai Gilgeous-Alexander scored 36 points, including 15 in the fourth quarter, and the Oklahoma City Thunder held on for a 101-93 victory over the Los Angeles Lakers in an NBA Cup game on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander scores 36 points as Thunder defeat Lakers 101-93 in NBA Cup game

events.name: Sacramento Kings at Portland Trail Blazers

headlines.description: — Deandre Ayton had 26 points and nine rebounds to lead the Portland Trail Blazers to a 115-106 victory over the Sacramento Kings in an NBA Cup game on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Trail Blazers beat Kings 115-106 to stay alive in NBA Cup
